title: Establishes the AgJobs NY program to provide low interest loans to finance certain costs of agribusinesses; appropriates $50,000,000
summary: Establishes the AgJobs NY program to provide low interest loans to finance certain costs of agribusinesses; appropriates $50,000,000.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the agriculture and markets law and the state finance law, in relation to establishing the AgJobs NY program; and making an appropriation therefor
